{"id": 1498, "genre": 1000, "title": "你是一个“错过很多信息也无所谓”的人吗？", "description": "JOMO，指的是当你拒绝参加一个聚会、一天不刷朋友圈，不会觉得错过了什么，反而很自在的情况。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 29701, "comment_count": 89, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170322101734F2BgbMSqWNc7C6Xd.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-16T17:00:24Z", "questions": [{"id": 1883, "title": "你是一个“错过很多信息也无所谓”的人吗？", "content": "你也有这些“社交JOMO”的症状吗？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 166548, "content": "新安装的App问你“是否允许推送”时，一律先选“否”", "image": "img/option/option/20170214145842eCrZgx3RPUAu4Y09.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 166553, "content": "邮件、短信、微信右上角小红点和三位数的未读通知，也觉得没什么", "image": "img/option/option/20170214151058W4ZktQo5fLRi2UJp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 166560, "content": "被拉进一个群聊，反应过来之后第一件事是设置“消息免打扰”", "image": "img/option/option/201702141526004yCwjGfoiWb07heU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 166566, "content": "绝不轻易关注新公众号，并定期把从不看的公众号取关", "image": "img/option/option/20170214153910ZK8jglkehNyq62tu.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 166573, "content": "屏蔽了一多半好友的朋友圈", "image": "img/option/option/20170214155509tMI4yiDZvHPplskc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 166574, "content": "不怎么刷手机，续航能有一天半", "image": "img/option/option/20170214155944xyOTK3F6oYBrfWZC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 166577, "content": "卸载了一些资讯类App，实在想知道什么的时候再上网搜", "image": "img/option/option/20170214161358poB0ibX6IL5dhUeV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}